# FCLIB contains the libraries for a CLINKER to use for code containing
# FORTRAN code (such as I/O or special Fortran runtimes).  
# The extra -lm is needed to force the C version of libm.a to 
# be searched before the Fortran 77 version.
#
FC_LIB         = /usr/lang/SC1.0.1/libF77.a -lm /usr/lang/SC1.0.1/libm.a 
#
